First should run a application after enter into productDemoApplication
then should type this "http://localhost:8080/productdemo" link in chrome for opening a database connection
after see all records in product table it will showing in h2 database
then hit a every api request following according to path name given 

for retrive all proudct data from given api 
this api will retrive all products = http://localhost:8080/products
for finding product by using id
first for get a product id use this api =http://localhost:8080/products/1  

for create a new product record 
http://localhost:8080/products

for update a product record from exisiting data base
http://localhost:8080/products/1

for delete operation
http://localhost:8080/products/1

find by category
http://localhost:8080/products/category/mobile

get available products sort by price
http://localhost:8080/products/available

release date after existing products
http://localhost:8080/products/released-after/2024-12-24

pagination
http://localhost:8080/products/list?pageNo=0&pageSize=10&sortBy=category

